OL,6,FA hosepipe ban which has been in place
OL,7,Facross Hampshire and the Isle of Wight
OL,8,Fsince July has now been lifted.
OL,10,FThe restriction on household water use
OL,11,Fwas introduced by Southern Water more
OL,12,Fthan three months ago, to help reduce
OL,13,Fpressure on the chalk streams of the
OL,14,FTest and Itchen rivers and make sure
OL,15,Ftaps kept running following prolonged
OL,16,Fdry weather.
