OL,6,FSouthern Water said the hosepipe ban
OL,7,Fhas helped to save millions of litres
OL,8,Fof water, boosted by wetter weather in
OL,9,FSeptember and October, and the fixing
OL,10,Fof leaks.
OL,12,FIt said around 1,700 leaks were
OL,13,Frepaired while the ban was in place `
OL,14,Fsaving more than 17 million litres of
OL,15,Fwater during that time.
