OL,6,FThe Test and Itchen ` which supply
OL,7,Fdrinking water to customers in
OL,8,FHampshire and the Isle of Wight - are
OL,9,Finternationally important rivers and
OL,10,Fhome to rare wildlife and delicate
OL,11,Fecosystems.
OL,13,FSouthern Water said reducing the need
OL,14,Fto abstract water from them during a
OL,15,Fvery dry period has been critical in
OL,16,Fprotecting them.
