OL,6,FTim McMahon, Southern Water's Director
OL,7,Fof Water, said:"We're incredibly
OL,8,Fgrateful to our customers for their
OL,9,Fsupport and understanding during this
OL,10,Fchallenging time.
OL,12,F"By working together, we've not only
OL,13,Fsaved millions of litres of water each
OL,14,Fday, but also helped protect our
OL,15,Fprecious chalk streams. This is a
OL,16,Fgreat example of how working together
OL,17,Fcan make a real difference to our
OL,18,Fenvironment."
