OL,6,FSouthern Water said it is working to
OL,7,Fbuild a more resilient water supply
OL,8,Ffor the future, developing alternative
OL,9,Fwater resources, including the UK's
OL,10,Ffirst new reservoir in over 30 years
OL,11,Fat Havant Thicket.
OL,13,FHowever, the National Drought Group
OL,14,Fhas warned of the risk of an ongoing
OL,15,Fdrought in 2026, unless there is
OL,16,Fsignificant rain this autumn and
OL,17,Fwinter.
OL,19,FThere are concerns about the country's
OL,20,Fwater resources because of this year's
OL,21,Frecord dry spring and warm summer.
