OL,6,FThe expert group - which includes the
OL,7,FMet Office, government, regulators,
OL,8,Fwater companies, the National Farmers'
OL,9,FUnion, Canal & River Trust, anglers,
OL,10,Fand conservation experts ` met this
OL,11,Fweek.
OL,13,FThey heard during an Environment
OL,14,FAgency presentation that England needs
OL,15,Fat least 100% of average rainfall
OL,16,F(482mm) to largely recover from
OL,17,Fdrought by the end of March next year.
OL,18,FThe south east received 126% in
OL,19,FSeptember.
