OL,6,FThe average reservoir storage is now
OL,7,F63.3% compared to the average for this
OL,8,Ftime of year of 76%. But Ardingly, in
OL,9,FWest Sussex was below 30%
OL,11,FThe very low level in Ardingly was the
OL,12,Freason the EA declared drought in
OL,13,Fparts of Sussex earlier this month,
OL,14,Fbut recent rainfall has helped.
OL,16,FSouth East Water (SEW) has submitted
OL,17,Ftwo Drought Orders to Defra. The
OL,18,Ffirst, for the River Ouse, and the
OL,19,Fsecond for a non-essential use ban
OL,20,Fwhich, if implemented, would see water
OL,21,Frestrictions on some businesses.
